StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.name: [GetEduca.onLevels]
StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.body:
AS
SET TRANSACTION ISOLATION LEVEL READ UNCOMMITTED
select educa.on_level_code as Code, educa.on_level_descrip.on as Descrip.on from mcriss.dbo.educa.on_level FOR XML PATH('Educa.onLevel'), ROOT('Educa.onLevels')
